<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Testimonials - VistaeGuide</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Header include -->
  <%- include("header.ejs") %>

  <main class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Page Header Section -->
      <section class="page-header">
        <h1>Student & Expert Testimonials</h1>
        <p>Hear from those who've walked the path before you</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Student Testimonials Grid -->
      <section class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">Choosing the science stream opened up a world of opportunities in tech for me. I'm now working on cutting-edge AI projects!</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-image">
              <img src="/7.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Priya Sharma">
            </div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <h3>Priya Sharma</h3>
              <p>Science Stream | Software Engineer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">The commerce stream gave me a strong foundation in finance. It's been crucial in my journey to becoming a CA.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-image">
              <img src="/8.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Rahul Patel">
            </div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <h3>Rahul Patel</h3>
              <p>Commerce Stream | Chartered Accountant</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">Studying arts honed my critical thinking and writing skills. It prepared me well for my career in journalism.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-image">
              <img src="/9.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Ananya Gupta">
            </div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <h3>Ananya Gupta</h3>
              <p>Arts Stream | Journalist</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="testimonial-quote">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i>
          </div>
          <p class="testimonial-text">The rigorous science curriculum was challenging but rewarding. It laid the groundwork for my medical career.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-image">
              <img src="/10.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Arjun Singh">
            </div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <h3>Arjun Singh</h3>
              <p>Science Stream | Doctor</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Expert Testimonials Section -->
      <section class="expert-testimonials">
        <h2>Expert Opinions</h2>
        <div class="expert-grid">
          <div class="expert-card">
            <div class="expert-image">
              <img src="/11.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Dr. Rajesh Kumar">
            </div>
            <div class="expert-content">
              <h3>Dr. Rajesh Kumar</h3>
              <p class="expert-title">Career Counselor, Delhi University</p>
              <p class="expert-quote">"Students should explore their interests before making a decision. The right stream aligns with both passion and aptitude."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="expert-card">
            <div class="expert-image">
              <img src="/12.jpeg?height=100&width=100" alt="Prof. Meena Sharma">
            </div>
            <div class="expert-content">
              <h3>Prof. Meena Sharma</h3>
              <p class="expert-title">Education Researcher, IIT Bombay</p>
              <p class="expert-quote">"The traditional boundaries between streams are blurring. Today's careers often require interdisciplinary knowledge."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Call to Action Section -->
      <section class="share-experience">
        <h2>Share Your Experience</h2>
        <p>Are you a former student who wants to share your journey? We'd love to hear from you! Please email us about your experience.</p>
        <a href="#footer" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer include -->
  <%- include("footer.ejs") %>

  <script src="main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
